\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8486024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 How many years did you live in the house you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2387616 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 When I was three years of age - we - had the house, took the house on.
