\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8486024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2387616 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 I've got four brothers and three sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8486024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 Could you tell me roughly their birth order or the spaces or the order they come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2387616 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 Well me eldest sister is in May. And she is seventy-six. And me brother - he is seventy-f
our. And I come next. And me other sister is - seventy - yes, just - just seventy. Just seventy. And there's - two years between the other brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8486024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 So he must be sixty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2387616 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 Yes. Then me other brother - four years in between.
