ge of life so that was - and quite nine years in between him. Brother, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8486024 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 So he's quite a youngster in fact?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2387616 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9247805\charrsid479496 Yes.
